article_id:1379,category_name:News,title_name:Halloween Mym Will Make Her Return! A Summon Showcase, Halloween Fantasia 2, Is Coming Back!,image_path:,message:<div>A Summon Showcase, Halloween Fantasia 2, is returning and kicks off <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1592546400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>The Summon Showcase will once again feature limited-time adventurers and dragons. Featured adventurers and dragons will also have a boosted appearance rate!</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The roster for this summon showcase does not include the newly added adventurers from the Nadine and Linnea&#39;s United Front summon showcase, which is live at the same time.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for featured summons:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1592546400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1593410340"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the featured adventurers and dragons returning for a limited time below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div>
